                    org.controlsfx.control.action.Action... actions)
        Creates notification.
        Parameters:
        messageType - Message type to be displayed on system tray.
        text - Notification text. Can be null.
        wrapLength - Wrapping length of text. Can be -1 for displaying text only for system tray messages.
        graphic - Notification graphic.
        hasTimer - True if notification has timer.
        isModal - True if this notification is modal.
        actions - Notification actions. Can be null.
